'''肯塔瑞里小堂'''（{{lang-it|Cappella Contarelli}}）为[[罗马|罗马]]的[[圣王路易堂|圣王路易堂]]内的左侧第一小堂，为富有的法国枢机主教玛窦·肯塔瑞里（Matthieu Cointerel）所有。肯塔瑞里小堂拥有该堂最著名的艺术品，系根据玛窦·肯塔瑞里的遗嘱，由[[巴洛克|巴洛克]]大师[[卡拉瓦乔|卡拉瓦乔]]在1599-1600年所画的[[瑪竇|瑪竇]]宗徒（马太）三幅生平系列画：《圣马太蒙召》、《圣马太与天使》和《圣马太殉教》。<ref name="smarth1">{{cite web | title =Caravaggio's paintings in the Contarelli Chapel, San Luigi dei Francesi | work = | publisher =Smarthistory at Khan Academy | date = | url =http://smarthistory.khanacademy.org/contarelli-chapel.html | accessdate =December 20, 2012 | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20130116124302/http://smarthistory.khanacademy.org/contarelli-chapel.html | archivedate =2013年1月16日 }}</ref><ref name="smarth2">{{cite web | title =Caravaggio's Calling of Saint Matthew | work = | publisher =Smarthistory at Khan Academy | date = | url =http://smarthistory.khanacademy.org/caravaggio-matthew.html | accessdate =December 20, 2012 | archive-date =2014-10-23 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20141023233737/http://smarthistory.khanacademy.org/caravaggio-matthew.html | dead-url =no }}</ref> 

